OL,3,CRetired teacher drowned in Storm Bert,
OL,4,Cinquest hears
OL,6,FA retired teacher drowned during Storm
OL,7,FBert, an inquest has heard.
OL,9,FA major search was launched when 75-
OL,10,Fyear-old Brian Perry was reported
OL,11,Fmissing after taking his dog for a
OL,12,Fwalk at the village of Trefriw, near
OL,13,FLlanrwst, during Storm Bert on 23
OL,14,FNovember.
OL,16,FAn inquest held on Thursday (20 March)
OL,17,Fheard that Mr Perry was overwhelmed by
OL,18,Ffast rising flood water at Gower Road,
OL,19,FTrefriw.
