OL,3,CRetired teacher drowned in Storm Bert,
OL,4,Cinquest hears
OL,6,FAfter a widespread emergency services
OL,7,Fresponse, his body was found the
OL,8,Ffollowing day submerged in water and
OL,9,Fthe death was confirmed at the scene
OL,10,Fon that date.
OL,12,FAt the opening of an inquest at Ruthin
OL,13,Fin December, John Gittins, senior
OL,14,Fcoroner for North Wales East and
OL,15,FCentral, said he had been informed by
OL,16,FNorth Wales Police that Mr Perry and
OL,17,Fhis wife Catherine set out together
OL,18,Fbut he then went on alone with the dog.
