OL,3,CRetired teacher drowned in Storm Bert,
OL,4,Cinquest hears
OL,6,FHe knew the area well and was wearing
OL,7,Fwaterproof clothing. Mr Gittins said
OL,8,FMrs Perry spoke to her husband on the
OL,9,Fphone but raised the alarm around 20
OL,10,Fminutes later when she no longer had a
OL,11,Freply.
OL,13,FThe coroner recorded a medical cause
OL,14,Fof death as drowning and ruled Mr
OL,15,FPerry's death as accidental.
OL,17,FA statement released by Mr Perry's
OL,18,Ffamily at the time of his death
OL,19,Fdescribed him as a "much-loved
OL,20,Fhusband, father, brother and
OL,21,Fgrandfather."
